  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,3,"Brothers and sisters, it is my privilege to present the General Authorities, Area Seventies, and General Officers of the Church for your sustaining vote."
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,4,"Please express your support in the usual way, wherever you may be. If there are those who oppose, we ask that you contact your stake president."
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,5,"It is proposed that we sustain Russell Marion Nelson as prophet, seer, and revelator and President of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints; Dallin Harris Oaks as First Counselor in the First Presidency; and Henry Bennion Eyring as Second Counselor in the First Presidency."
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,6,Those in favor may manifest it.
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,7,"Those opposed, if any, may manifest it."
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,8,It is proposed that we sustain Dallin H. Oaks as President of the Quorum of the Twelve Apostles and M. Russell Ballard as Acting President of the Quorum of the Twelve Apostles.
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,9,"Those in favor, please signify."
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,10,Any opposed may manifest it.
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,11,"It is proposed that we sustain the following as the members of the Quorum of the Twelve Apostles: M. Russell Ballard, Jeffrey R. Holland, Dieter F. Uchtdorf, David A. Bednar, Quentin L. Cook, D. Todd Christofferson, Neil L. Andersen, Ronald A. Rasband, Gary E. Stevenson, Dale G. Renlund, Gerrit W. Gong, and Ulisses Soares."
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,12,"Those in favor, please manifest it."
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,13,Any opposed may so indicate.
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,14,"It is proposed that we sustain the counselors in the First Presidency and the Quorum of the Twelve Apostles as prophets, seers, and revelators."
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,15,"All in favor, please manifest it."
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,16,"Contrary, if there be any, by the same sign."
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,17,"As announced previously, we have extended a call to Alexander Dushku to serve as a General Authority Seventy."
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,18,"Those in favor, please manifest it."
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,19,"Those opposed, by the same sign."
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,20,We also note with appreciationthe releases of two Area Seventies whose names can be found on the Church’s website.
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,21,Those who wish to join in expressing gratitude to these brethren for their excellent service may manifest it.
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,22,"It is proposed that we sustain the other General Authorities and Area Seventies, including two new Area Seventies announced earlier this week whose names are listed on the Church’s website, and the General Officers as presently constituted."
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,23,All in favor may do so by the uplifted hand.
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,24,"Those opposed, if any."
