  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/28rasband,Elder Ronald A. Rasband,53,"Senior missionary opportunities take many forms, and couples or senior sisters may list preferences as well as a full-time or Church-service assignment. Ultimately, the prophet of the Church issues the call for full-time service. Stake presidents issue Church-service assignments. Service can range from 6 months to 23 months, and senior missionaries have more flexibility and less strenuous activity than young missionaries. Seeseniormissionary.ChurchofJesusChrist.org."
  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/28rasband,Elder Ronald A. Rasband,54,"Russell M. Nelson, “Senior Missionaries and the Gospel,”EnsignorLiahona, Nov. 2004, 79."
