  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/53cordon,Elder Valeri V. Cordón,28,"This may seem like a daunting task, but as Elder Jeffrey R. Holland said, “With a Heavenly Father’s help we can leave more of a parental legacy than we suppose” (“The Hands of the Fathers,”Ensign, May 1999, 15;Liahona, July 1999, 18)."
