  2023,"10",/general-conference/2023/10/53cordon,Elder Valeri V. Cordón,48,"See Russell M. Nelson, “Salvation and Exaltation,”EnsignorLiahona, May 2008, 10: “Do not try to control your children. Instead, listen to them, help them to learn the gospel, inspire them, and lead them toward eternal life. You are God’s agents in the care of children He has entrusted to you. Let His divine influence remain in your hearts as you teach and persuade.”"
